  "modules": [
    {
      "type": "resource/model/language",
      "data": {
        "name": "Llama 3.3 70B Instruct",
        "version": "3.3-70B-Instruct",
        "size": "70B",
        "description": "# Llama 3.3 70B Instruct\n\nMeta's flagship open-weight instruction-tuned model, strong at reasoning, math, and multilingual tasks. Distributed with reproducible GGUF and Ollama artifacts for local execution.\n\n## Features\n- **Long context**: 128K tokens.\n- **Tool calling**: Native function calling and parallel tool calls.\n- **Multilingual**: Trained on 8 languages.\n\n## Getting Started\n```\nollama pull llama3.3:70b-instruct-q4_K_M\nollama serve\n```\nOnce running, the model is reachable at `http://localhost:11434/v1` using the OpenAI-compatible API.",
        "deployments": [
          {
            "mode": "local",
            "endpoint": {
              "url": "http://localhost:11434/v1",
              "type": "openai",
              "protocol": "https"
            },
            "env_vars": [
              {
                "name": "OLLAMA_HOST",
                "description": "Host and port for the local Ollama daemon.",
                "required": false
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "context": {
          "max_input_tokens": 128000,
          "max_output_tokens": 8192,
          "max_total_tokens": 128000
        },
        "trained_at": "2026-01-15T00:00:00Z",
        "supported_languages": [
          "en-US",
          "es-ES",
          "fr-FR",
          "de-DE",
          "hi-IN",
          "th-TH",
          "pt-BR",
          "it-IT"
        ],
        "artifacts": [
          {
            "type": "application/vnd.ollama.image.model",
            "url": "https://ollama.com/library/llama3.3:70b-instruct-q4_K_M"
          }
        ]
      },
      "modules": [
        {
          "type": "traits/quality/evaluation",
          "data": {
            "evaluations": [
              {
                "benchmark": "MMLU",
                "benchmark_url": "https://github.com/hendrycks/test",
                "metric": "accuracy",
                "score": 0.86,
                "unit": "ratio",
                "evaluator": "Meta",
                "evaluated_at": "2026-01-10T00:00:00Z",
                "source_url": "https://ai.meta.com/blog/llama-3-3"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "resource/model/language",
      "data": {
        "name": "Qwen 2.5 Coder 7B Instruct",
        "version": "2.5-Coder-7B-Instruct",
        "size": "7B",
        "description": "# Qwen 2.5 Coder 7B Instruct\n\nCode-focused open-weight model from Alibaba; strong fill-in-the-middle and repo-level completion. Designed to run on a single consumer GPU or Apple Silicon device.\n\n## Features\n- **Code Generation**: Trained on a large multi-language code corpus.\n- **Long context**: 131K tokens.\n- **Function calling**: OpenAI-compatible tool schemas.\n\n## Getting Started\n```\nllama-server -hf Qwen/Qwen2.5-Coder-7B-Instruct-GGUF -c 32768\n```\nEndpoint: `http://localhost:8080/v1`.",
        "deployments": [
          {
            "mode": "local",
            "endpoint": {
              "url": "http://localhost:8080/v1",
              "type": "openai",
              "protocol": "https"
            },
            "env_vars": [
              {
                "name": "LLAMA_ARG_MODEL",
                "description": "Path or Hugging Face id of the GGUF file to load in llama.cpp server.",
                "required": false
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "mode": "local",
            "endpoint": {
              "url": "http://localhost:8080/v1",
              "type": "openai",
              "protocol": "https"
            },
            "env_vars": [
              {
                "name": "MLX_MODEL",
                "description": "Hugging Face id of the MLX-quantized model to serve (e.g. mlx-community/Qwen2.5-Coder-7B-Instruct-4bit).",
                "required": false
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "context": {
          "max_input_tokens": 131072,
          "max_output_tokens": 8192,
          "max_total_tokens": 131072
        },
        "trained_at": "2025-11-12T00:00:00Z",
        "supported_languages": ["en-US", "zh-Hans"],
        "artifacts": [
          {
            "type": "application/vnd.gguf.v3",
            "url": "https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen2.5-Coder-7B-Instruct-GGUF/resolve/main/qwen2.5-coder-7b-instruct-q4_k_m.gguf"
          }
        ]
      },
      "modules": [
        {
          "type": "traits/quality/evaluation",
          "data": {
            "evaluations": [
              {
                "benchmark": "HumanEval",
                "benchmark_url": "https://github.com/openai/human-eval",
                "metric": "pass@1",
                "score": 0.884,
                "unit": "ratio",
                "evaluator": "Qwen Team",
                "evaluated_at": "2025-11-10T00:00:00Z",
                "source_url": "https://qwenlm.github.io/blog/qwen2.5-coder"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "resource/model/language",
      "data": {
        "name": "Mistral 7B Instruct v0.3",
        "version": "7B-Instruct-v0.3",
        "size": "7B",
        "description": "# Mistral 7B Instruct v0.3\n\nCompact general-purpose open-weight model from Mistral AI. A solid baseline for on-device chat, RAG, and function calling.\n\n## Features\n- **Compact**: Runs on 8 GB of RAM (Q4_K_M).\n- **Function calling**: v0.3 adds native tool schemas.\n- **Multilingual**: English, French, German, Spanish, Italian.\n\n## Getting Started\n```\nollama pull mistral:7b-instruct-v0.3-q4_K_M\n```",
        "deployments": [
          {
            "mode": "local",
            "endpoint": {
              "url": "http://localhost:11434/v1",
              "type": "openai",
              "protocol": "https"
            },
            "env_vars": [
              {
                "name": "OLLAMA_HOST",
                "description": "Host and port for the local Ollama daemon.",
                "required": false
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "context": {
          "max_input_tokens": 32768,
          "max_output_tokens": 8192,
          "max_total_tokens": 32768
        },
        "trained_at": "2024-05-22T00:00:00Z",
        "supported_languages": ["en-US", "fr-FR", "de-DE", "es-ES", "it-IT"],
        "artifacts": [
          {
            "type": "application/vnd.gguf.v3",
            "url": "https://huggingface.co/mistralai/Mistral-7B-Instruct-v0.3-GGUF/resolve/main/mistral-7b-instruct-v0.3.Q4_K_M.gguf"
          }
        ]
      },
      "modules": [
        {
          "type": "traits/quality/evaluation",
          "data": {
            "evaluations": [
              {
                "benchmark": "MT-Bench",
                "benchmark_url": "https://github.com/lm-sys/FastChat",
                "metric": "score",
                "score": 7.5,
                "unit": "1-10",
                "evaluator": "Mistral AI",
                "evaluated_at": "2024-05-22T00:00:00Z",
                "source_url": "https://mistral.ai/news/announcing-mistral-7b-v0-3"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
